{"__ud_title":"Web3 Notes 应用","__ud_tags":[],"__ud_update_time":1747836062581,"__ud_create_time":1745403531295,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"Web3-Notes-应用"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Web3 Notes 应用"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"定义"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"DeFi"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"点对点金融"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"钱包、借贷、稳定币、预言机、交易、衍生品期权、资产信息"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"数据、跨链、保险"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"NFT"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Punk#5822藏品"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"非同质化代币，每个都是独一无二的。可以映射艺术品或土地"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"游戏"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"AXIE"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"DAO"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"去中心化自治组织"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"将治理规则以智能合约的形式编码上链，使参与者能够就组织资源、事项执行、资金分配等事项投票出共识决策"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"协议型、应用型、资源分配型"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"DID身份 隐私"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"泛指去中心化数字身份"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"web3中 区块链地址"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"简单来说就是对你建立的地址进行赋能。是web2 用户画像概念在web3中的延伸拓展"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"应用层：1、Reputation 可信任标签化"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2、Relationship 基于用户在Web3数据的累积的数字身份，来做复杂综合的应用分析"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"数据层："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"链上数据：转账、DeFi交互、NFT交易 一切链上行为。但无法验证真人"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"链下数据：Web2身份、PoP、SBT"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"身份层："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"应用场景和数据的连接"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1、信息聚合协议：对链上原始数据、各种凭证数据的加工聚合"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2、身份管理工具：钱包地址、域名等"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"凭证层"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"跨链、多链"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"以太、BNB智能链、btc链"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"每个链，有自己的通信协议共识规则和治理模型。可以比方成一个城市。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"跨链就是打通各个城市间的阻碍，实现价值交换"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"跨交易和跨消息"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"特定资产跨链、特定链跨链（解锁锁定token）、特定应用跨链、通用型跨链互调合约（链直接的信息通信）"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"行业基础设施"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Chainlink 预言机：预测现实世界实时的数据，将外部的信息写入到区块链内。主要用于区块链和外部世界的沟通。ORACLE Contract 通过调用外部聚合API把数据返回到链上。比如提供以太坊的实时价格"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Alchemy ： 区块链界的 AWS 阿里云"}]}]}